import { useState } from "react"; import "form.scss" const Form = () => { const [data, setData] = useState({ firstName: "", lastName: "", email: "", birthDate: Date.now(), city: "", zip: "", }); return (
setData({ ...data, lastName: event.target.value }) } />
setData({ ...data, firstName: event.target.value }) } />
setData({ ...data, email: event.target.value })} />
setData({ ...data, birthDate: event.target.value }) } />
setData({ ...data, city: event.target.value })} />
setData({ ...data, zip: event.target.value })} />
); }; export default Form;
